what is a good haircut for a round face and long hair it would help if you add pictures too drew barrymore has a round face you can google her look at images of different styles she's had but in general like the square face this full face which features a round hairline and chin line and marks its widest point at the cheeks benefits greatly from the illusion of length when dealing with a round face it's best to create fullness and height at the crown while keeping the rest of the hair close to the face to avoid adding any additional width to the sides of the cheeks like the square face those with round faces should avoid center parts and linear bangs although bangs brushed to the side are flattering haircuts that end at the chin line should also be avoided as they will only emphasize the roundness of the face Haircut Hair Archery Beard Vitruvian Man Glossary of partner dance terms Stairway Dominoes Ra (board game) Professional wrestling throws Shaving Boxing Baldness Drawing Marching band Draw poker Maxilla Mahjong Toronto Blue Jays Poker jargon Betting (poker) Drill bit Motorcycle helmet Physical attractiveness Eigenvalue, eigenvector and eigenspace Wallpaper group Diving Head Physical characteristics of the Buddha Norway national football team Colours, standards and guidons Blackjack Diamond cut Rigging Barber Face Panoramic photography Parallax Trigonometric function Aberration in optical systems Griffon Bruxellois Cathedral architecture Mixed martial arts Cat Professional wrestling holds Violin Emo fashion Textile manufacturing Laws of cricket Antenna (radio) Moustache Brush Spark plug JPEG Internal ballistics Autostereogram Fielding (cricket) Linked list Butterfly stroke Irish Houses of Parliament Chu shogi Vowel Circle Social role of hair Oakland Athletics Tefillin Stud poker Maya calendar Ruler-and-compass construction Fast bowling Big Bang Hash table Sydney Harbour Bridge Trumpet B-24 Liberator Glossary of American football My Little Pony CPU cache Dai shogi